ny time you can reduce something by 1,000x-10,000x &#8230; that&#8217;s a p=
retty big deal. And when that thing your reducing by 1,000x-10,000x has to =
do with training AI models, welp, that&#8217;s a very big deal.</p><p style=
=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0=
 20px 0;">DisTrO works by reducing the amount of data that needs to be shar=
